{
  "stem": "4226.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were burned, black hole like outside.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But then we distributed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody got two potatoes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when they counted you in the freezing morning, kept your warm in your pockets, two hot potatoes.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Plus you, you ate it, too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The middle didn't burn.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Only the outside.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now these, these Germans gave us German mark distributed for different groups in BMW and where we worked.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We got here sometimes 50 marks, sometimes 200 mark for the 50.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So the capo-- he was a Yugoslav man-- he said, we've got 100 mark.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Two mark each for the group.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we didn't get the money.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They had a canteen inside the camp which sold goods which you couldn't use.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Sold you pen and pencil.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You can't write a letter to anybody.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You could do drawings with it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And very seldom, like for Christmas, they had some cheap lollies in there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So you can buy-- they were given one mark only to spend on lollies in there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You had a card in, in the canteen with the amount of money your group earned.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then they deducted whatever you bought there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They had shoe cream.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, you had wooden shoes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Who, who cared about cleaning shoes?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nobody bought it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So it was a-- was really a--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Useless things.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They called it canteen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was useless, completely useless.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But there-- it was there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now in, in the beginning we get 600 gram bread, which was quite a lot of bread for a prisoner, which went down slowly to four people a bread.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Bread was total 800 gram.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then six and then eight in the end.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were shortages.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] What can I also tell you from Allach?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Were they trying to starve you?",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
